      <title>南苏丹打击平行外汇市场以对抗通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/south-sudan-cracks-down-on-parallel-fx-market-to-fight-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南苏丹打击了首都朱巴的外汇交易商，该国最高央行行长表示，此举是稳定其快速贬值货币的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/south-sudan-cracks-down-on-parallel-fx-market-to-fight-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 17:22:37 GMT</pubDate>
