      <title>塞尔维亚总统武契奇任命国防部长武切维奇为候任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/serbia-president-picks-party-chief-and-loyalist-as-new-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚总统亚历山大·武契奇在大选巩固权力后三个多月，提名他的盟友兼副总理担任该国新政府领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/serbia-president-picks-party-chief-and-loyalist-as-new-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 16:09:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将恢复限制太阳能进口以提振当地生产商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/india-brings-back-curbs-on-solar-panel-imports-to-boost-locals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在放宽一年的限制后，印度将重新对进口太阳能组件实施限制，这让那些抱怨海外发货更便宜的国内制造商松了一口气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/india-brings-back-curbs-on-solar-panel-imports-to-boost-locals</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 15:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁当局因劳力士丑闻突袭博卢阿特住宅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/peru-authorities-raided-boluarte-s-residence-amid-rolex-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁当局突击搜查了总统迪娜·博卢阿特 (Dina Boluarte) 的住所，作为对她非法致富调查的一部分，因为她在公共场合佩戴豪华手表的丑闻日益严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/peru-authorities-raided-boluarte-s-residence-amid-rolex-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 13:14:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国反恐警察调查伦敦记者遇袭事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/uk-counterterrorism-police-investigate-an-attack-on-a-television-presenter-outside-his-london-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦（美联社）——英国反恐警察正在调查一名伊朗电视节目主持人在伦敦家外被刺伤的事件，因为人们越来越担心长期批评伊朗神权政府的波斯语卫星新闻频道受到的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/uk-counterterrorism-police-investigate-an-attack-on-a-television-presenter-outside-his-london-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 11:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
